init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: “I’m going to be honest with you,” she says.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: “I’ve been with a lot of guys, and I’ve never felt this way.”

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: “I think I’m falling in love with you too,” Truman replied.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She opened it, and there stood Truman.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I've been waiting for you to realize I'm the one."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You're the guy I've been dating?" she asked.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She took it and read the label.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I don't know what to say," she said.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She opened her eyes, and saw that she had transformed into a man.
